          <h3>NSF Certified for Sport</h3>
          <p>The strongest seal in sports supplements. Required for collegiate athletes (NCAA, FIFA, MLB, NFL, NHL) and confirms product is free of banned substances and matches label claims.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-card-ico">IS</div>
          <h3>Informed Sport / Informed Choice</h3>
          <p>UK-based testing program with batch-level verification used by professional teams worldwide. Equivalent rigor to NSF for the testing population it targets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <div class="info-card-ico">USP</div>
          <h3>USP Verified</h3>
          <p>United States Pharmacopeia verification — independent confirmation of identity, potency, purity, and dissolution. The pharmaceutical-grade quality standard for supplements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
